{"tid":2461013,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得真係時代變","createTime":"2021-03-25T07:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T07:39:45.000Z","uid":307910,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd821b1982ca14776bf584c522e6b3a9feaff52","tid":2461013,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"喺我個年代<br />\n余文樂同周柏豪都so called 叫做天皇巨星<br />\n<br />\n前者喺00年代拍唔少電影做小生隔離嘅配角，仲係之後擔正，開始拍咗志明系列，紅遍中港台，跟佢著衫係型嘅表現，大家都知佢打波叻，仲要大隻靚仔<br />\n呢個食一批target fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周柏豪就唱歌起家，一事無成成為當時90後嘅神曲（twins係八十後），無論k房，年輕人聚集嘅潮特，無一唔播pakho嘅歌，之後喺樂壇都叫做中流砥柱，去到2013－4更加係佢嘅事業高峰，一手我的宣言，感動萬代千少女，大把人結婚男方都跪係度唱贈你一吻或許容易，外型更加唔洗講，行靚仔路線又得，型格路線都得，仲要坐擁一米82嘅身高<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個人可謂當時娛樂圈一時無兩嘅代表人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家淪落成卻過街老鼠，同人講話鍾意牙Shawn同pakho 會俾人笑到面黃<br />\n<br />\n究竟佢哋幾時可以重奪娛樂圈嘅一哥地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為佢哋嘅fans心急人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8519be07f25009eeeea2c2b7f9bd17939f2aa103","tid":2461013,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3e59f5befe40dbaf68e59db85ac0c1c05a7f32","tid":2461013,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"我以前對Kelly 唱過我的宣言表白架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cfca59337a780ddeba166b7eeba28e2ef1b283","tid":2461013,"uid":30